HEADWORD: Incalescent
<hw>In`ca*les"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>incalescens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of
<ets>incalescere</ets> to grow hot. See 1st <er>In-</er>, and
<er>Calescence</er>.]</ety> <def>Growing warm; increasing in
